I agree that transformers moving protohumans might be a bad idea because of 
the whole time thing, but what if another transformer-like race began doing 
it.  It would make for an interesting plot.  I want ideas about this, not 
opinions, LN that means no saying that's stupid unless you want to suggest 
something better to the whole group.  If you think this idea is terrible I 
want a better idea.
